    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm selling my absolute pride and joy, and let me tell you, she is a total dream! This car is in truly spectacular condition\u2014honestly, it\u2019s like it just rolled off the showroom floor. I\u2019ve babied it from day one, keeping it garage-kept and sparkling clean inside and out. It drives perfectly and has been super reliable. If you're looking for a ride that feels and looks brand new, you've found it! I'm sad to see it go, but I'm excited for it to find a great new home. Drop me a message if you want to come take a look!",
      "price": 44500.0,
