      "timestep_posted": 16
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offering a museum-grade E46 M3, this specimen features the legendary S54 inline-six with a fully documented VANOS overhaul and reinforced rear subframe. The powertrain remains in peak mechanical health, delivering linear power through the Getrag 6-speed manual and a tight limited-slip differential. Suspension geometry is factory-perfect with fresh bushings, ensuring the chassis handles with the precision intended by the M-division. Zero aesthetic blemishes or mechanical fatigue; this is a turnkey collector-grade vehicle for the discerning enthusiast.",
      "price": 48500.0,
