    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional example of automotive preservation. This vehicle remains in showroom-fresh condition, having been meticulously stored in a climate-controlled environment since new. The exterior paint retains its deep, mirror-like luster with zero imperfections, protected by a professional ceramic coating. Inside, the cabin is indistinguishable from the day it left the factory; the premium leather remains supple with no visible wear on the bolsters, and the original interior scent lingers. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach, accompanied by a comprehensive, documented service history from authorized dealers only. Every button, switch, and electronic feature operates with factory precision. This is a rare opportunity for a collector or discerning driver to acquire a turnkey masterpiece that looks, feels, and drives as if it just rolled off the assembly line. No stones unturned, no flaws to hide\u2014just pure excellence.",
